    • CreateCollectiveView

      public CreateCollectiveView()
      Constructor of CreateCollectiveView: Initializes all the attributes and puts them in the right places in the container of the window. It is mainly formed by one tabs, a cancel button and a cancel button. The tab gives the user all the options to create a new collective.
